<figureCitation id="099BFB7DC24177D23E0419206ACB579C" captionStart="Plate 10" captionStartId="F10" captionText="Plate 10. 59. Colotis evagore nouna f. vernalis alticola auresiaca (Stauder, 1913); 60. Colotis evagore nouna f. biformata (Stauder, 1913); 61. Colotis evagore nouna f. aestiva pyroleuca (Stauder, 1913); 62. Colotis evagore nouna ab. evagorides (Stauder, 1913); 63. Pieris brassicae italorum Stauder, 1921; 64. Pieris ergane elbursina Bytinski-Salz &amp; Brandt, 1937; 65. Pieris ergane r. exigua Verity, 1923. a. Dorsal view, b. ventral view." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579719" pageId="0" pageNumber="193">65</figureCitation>
